From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 26 May 2025 18:02:51 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 02/11] QSDK:DP:wifi: ath12k: Add DS node id retrieval
 mechanism

The node ID is used between the PPE module and the WIFI module
to identify the unique radios in the system. The wifi driver
returns the DS node as a result for the ECM path lookup to let
the PPE driver know where the packets should be forwarded

DS feature requires ath_dp_accel_cfg.h to be used by both nss-ecm and ath module.
This file is created by ath module and copy to staging dir to get accessed by
nss-ecm module

Patch-dependency:
	325-QSDK-DP-wifi-Add-support-for-PPE-DS-Direct-switch-fe.patch
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
